1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: lpf.c,v 1.8 2002/06/09 03:56:29 millert Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: lpf.c,v 1.8 2000/04/29 00:12:32 abs Exp $	*/

